WEBVTT

1
00:24:25.310 --> 00:24:27.700 
除非确定你的症状非复发性的
What happenedwas a non-recurring event.

2
00:24:27.700 --> 00:24:29.890 
单凭你说自己没事是不解决问题的
Saying you feel fine doesn't solve this.

3
00:24:36.620 --> 00:24:39.600 
能跟我讲讲医患保密协议吗
Would you tell me about patient confidentiality?

4
00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:41.070 
你很直接
It's very straightforward.

5
00:24:41.070 --> 00:24:42.050 
未经你同意
Without your permission,

6
00:24:42.050 --> 00:24:44.400 
我不得向任何人透露你我谈话内容
I can't disclose anything you tell me to anyone.

7
00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:45.930 
我的亲属呢
What about my family?

8
00:24:45.930 --> 00:24:48.410 
亲属  警方  任何人都不可以
Not your family, not to the police. Not to anyone.

9
00:24:49.540 --> 00:24:52.400 
除非你威胁要杀死某人
The only exception would be if you threatened to kill someone.

10
00:24:52.400 --> 00:24:55.480 
那样我可以告诉被威胁者  也仅限被威胁者
Then I'd be able to tell that person, but only that person.

